c: 2
v: 114
t: "la ahd 'azlam min aladhin manaeuu dhikr allah fi almasajid min 'iqam alslat, wtlawt alqran, wanahw dhlk, wjddu fi tkhrybha balhdm 'aw al'ighlaq, 'aw bimane almuminin mnha. 'uwlayik alzaalimun ma kan yanbaghi lahum 'ana ydkhlu almasajid 'iilaa ealaa khawf wwjl min aleqwbt, lahum bdhlk saghar wfdyht fi aldnya, walahum fi alakhirat eadhab shdyd"